  <brief_title>Lidocaine as Local Anesthetics in Children Under Ketamine Sedation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Lidocaine as Local Anesthetics in Children Under Procedural Sedation and Analgesia Using Ketamine</official_title>
  <sponsors>
